query:
INSERT INTO trips (
                    id,
                    name,
                    slug,
                    year,
                    description,
                    created_at,
                    user_id
                ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
                ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE 
                SET 
                    name = EXCLUDED.name,
                    slug = EXCLUDED.slug,
                    year = EXCLUDED.year,
                    description = EXCLUDED.description
